# Shell scripts must have LF line endings — bash on Linux (incl. act's CI
# containers) treats CR as part of the command, breaking `set -euo pipefail`
# and every other line. Windows checkouts with core.autocrlf=true would
# otherwise rewrite these with CRLF on clone.
*.sh text eol=lf
